GNOME Utilities - "The Piccolo Snare"
=====================================
Version: 2.15.90

Warning ! This is an unstable version.

GNOME Utilities for the GNOME 2.15 Desktop contains the following -

	gnome-system-log	[logview]
	gnome-search-tool	[gseachtool]
	gnome-dictionary	[gnome-dictionary]
	gfloppy			[gfloppy]
	gnome-screenshot	[gnome-screenshot]
	baobab                  [baobab]

Requirements -

	intltool	>= 0.34.90
	gnome-common	>= 2.3.0
	glib		>= 2.9.1
	gtk+            >= 2.8.0
	libgnome	>= 2.13.7
	libgnomeui	>= 2.13.2
	gnome-desktop   >= 2.9.91
	libglade	>= 2.3.0
	libbonoboui	>= 2.1.0
	libgnomevfs	>= 2.8.4
	libpanel-applet >= 2.13.4
	libgnomeprintui >= 2.8.0
	libgtop         >= 2.12.0
	libgnomecanvas  >= 2.10.2


The following configure flags can be used -

  --enable-console-helper=no/yes  Enable PAM console helper [default=no]
  --enable-hal=yes/no             Enable HAL support for gfloppy [default=yes]	
  --with-grep                     Specify the path to the grep
                                  command [default=find it ourselves]

Installation -

See the file 'INSTALL'

How to report bugs -

See the file 'BUGS'
